videos.headline: Oregon's Verdell extends lead with short TD
videos.description: CJ Verdell runs for 56 yards on a drive that he finishes off with a 1-yard touchdown to pad Oregon's lead vs. Oregon State.

videos.headline: Oregon RB Verdell scores hat trick in 1st half
videos.description: Justin Herbert throws a 34-yard completion on a tipped pass, then CJ Verdell scores for the third time in the first half vs. Oregon State.

videos.headline: Oregon State's Luton tosses dime for TD
videos.description: Jake Luton drops it in the bucket to Timmy Hernandez for a 22-yard completion that is ruled a touchdown after review.

videos.headline: Verdell's 4th TD goes for 14 yards
videos.description: Oregon's defense recovers a fumble and CJ Verdell takes advantage with a 14-yard touchdown run, his 4th score vs. Oregon State.

videos.headline: Oregon takes INT to the house
videos.description: Jake Luton's pass is intercepted by Thomas Graham Jr. and he returns it 38 yards for a touchdown in the 4th quarter.

videos.headline: Oregon RB Dye runs for 39-yard TD
videos.description: Travis Dye runs behind his lead blockers and finds daylight for a 39-yard touchdown to continue Oregon's rout over Oregon State.

videos.headline: Verdell plunges ahead for 5th TD
videos.description: CJ Verdell scores his fifth touchdown vs. Oregon State, this time from one yard away to increase Oregon's lead in the 4th quarter.

videos.headline: Oregon State's tricky play turns into a disaster
videos.description: Oregon State attempts a trick play, but it does not go as planned and Oregon's Gus Cumberlander jumps on the fumble.
